These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, lilac, apricot, yellow
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the australian and the person who likes white##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | white    | apricot      | lilac      | yellow    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting, skateboarding, handball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | skateboarding   | snowboarding | handball |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, orange, lilac
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee  | fanta    | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Color         | aquamarine    | lilac | brown | orange  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dunhill, ritmeester, game
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is between the person watching drama movies and the fonseca-smoker##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the game-smoker##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the game-smoker is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar          | ritmeester   | fonseca     | dunhill | game |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| Pet           | turtle | lizard      | goat     | dog       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, purple, light-blue, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance, western
1. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
3. the lawyer is the person watching action movies##1
4. the architect is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes purple##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
8. the person who likes light-blue is the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Color          | light-blue      | orange | purple      | apricot |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | western   | drama     | action   |

