.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, fonseca, baccarat, ritmeester
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the coach##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| Cigar   | bongani     | baccarat   | ritmeester         | fonseca        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

