.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, davidoff, bluemaster, baccarat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, egyptian, mexican
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the egyptian##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | davidoff   | bluemaster | prince | baccarat |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Nationality   | canadian | chinese   | egyptian    | mexican   |

