.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
House: victorian, wooden, craftsman, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, rowing, skateboarding
1. the lawyer is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the victorian house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the victorian house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
7. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| House   | wooden             | victorian     | gothic-revival | craftsman  |
| Sport         | lacrosse           | skateboarding | biathlon   | rowing |

