.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, entrepreneur, photographer, pilot
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, snake, turtle
1. the pilot is on the left or right of the photographer##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the turtle is between the pilot and the person drinking soy-milk##2
5. the pilot is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the dancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | dancer | photographer | pilot      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate       | lemonade  |
| Pet           | rat          | snake  | turtle       | guinea-pig |

