.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, blueberry, cranberry, plum
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, lilac, grey
1. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
2. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person who likes lilac is the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person who likes ebony is between the person eating avocado and the person eating cranberry##2
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cranberry | blueberry  | avocado  | plum           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Color   | grey   | ebony       | blood-red | lilac  |

 